25	Artemether	antimalarial,artemisinin,derivative,Plasmodium,intramuscular	Artemether is an artemisinin derivative used to treat severe malaria, often administered intramuscularly. It rapidly kills malaria parasites by producing free radicals from heme within infected red blood cells.
26	Artermether + Lumefantrine	antimalarial,ACT,pediatric,dispersible,Plasmodium	Artermether + Lumefantrine (Artemether + Lumefantrine) is an artemisinin-based combination therapy available in dispersible tablet form for pediatric use in treating uncomplicated malaria.
