019d8bc3-60de-7338-9498-95be6cbcce62	Doppler Scan	Radiology	Imaging	{D,SM}	Ultrasound assessment of blood flow velocity and direction in vessels for vascular disease diagnosis.
019d8bc3-60de-7347-bb73-57584b2141e4	EEG (Electroencephalogram)	Neurology	Procedure	{D,SM}	Records electrical activity of the brain for diagnosis of epilepsy, seizures, and encephalopathy.
019d8bc3-60de-735a-af0e-4d7dbb62710e	Estrogen	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures estradiol levels for fertility assessment, menopause evaluation, and hormone therapy monitoring.
019d8bc3-60de-7362-94ce-ba8ebd2fd7be	Factor IX	Haematology	Lab	{D,SM}	Quantifies Factor IX clotting factor levels for diagnosis and monitoring of hemophilia B.
019d8bc3-60de-736f-89cf-5eee7196c97c	Factor VIII	Haematology	Lab	{D,SM}	Quantifies Factor VIII clotting factor levels for diagnosis and monitoring of hemophilia A.
019d8bc3-60de-737b-bce5-ed9d42abdaf4	Follicle Stimulating Hormone (FSH)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures FSH levels for infertility assessment, menopause evaluation, and pituitary function.
019d8bc3-60de-7385-9aaa-ace9ef1bf3e8	FT3	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Free Triiodothyronine - measures active thyroid hormone for thyroid function assessment.
019d8bc3-60de-7390-9d4a-32e7f36f1b54	FT4	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Free Thyroxine - measures active thyroid hormone for thyroid function assessment.
019d8bc3-60de-739a-bd72-ee6e58b1747c	Guthrie test	Newborn Screening	Lab	{D,SM}	Newborn blood spot screening for phenylketonuria, hypothyroidism, and other metabolic disorders.
019d8bc3-60de-73a5-90c9-7a706f233049	Holter	Cardiology	Procedure	{D,SM}	24-48 hour continuous ECG monitoring for detection of intermittent arrhythmias and cardiac events.
019d8bc3-60de-73b2-8095-7500a6f55d9b	Human Immunodeficiency Virus (HIV) Confirmation	Microbiology	Lab	{D,SM}	Confirmatory test (Western blot or PCR) for HIV infection after positive screening test.
019d8bc3-60de-73bd-9d54-d272facef857	Immunostaining	Immunology	Lab	{D,SM}	Immunohistochemistry or immunofluorescence for detection of specific antigens in tissue sections.
019d8bc3-60de-73c9-b9c0-2642185b6910	Intravenous Urography	Radiology	Imaging	{D,SM}	Contrast study of kidneys, ureters, and bladder (IVU/IVP) for urinary tract assessment.
019d8bc3-60de-73d5-a1ef-579311104b7e	Luteinizing Hormone (LH)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures LH levels for fertility assessment, ovulation timing, and pituitary function evaluation.
019d8bc3-60de-73df-8b60-2b42579bdf47	Mammogram	Radiology	Imaging	{D,SM}	Low-dose X-ray of breast tissue for breast cancer screening and diagnostic evaluation.
019d8bc3-60de-73ed-a78d-9f7623ee1daa	MRI - 1 Region + No Contrast	Radiology	Imaging	{D,SM}	Magnetic resonance imaging of one region without contrast for detailed soft tissue evaluation.
019d8bc3-60de-73fa-b648-c1a617e6f7de	MRI - 1 Region + Contrast	Radiology	Imaging	{D,SM}	MRI with gadolinium contrast for enhanced visualization of tumors, inflammation, and vascular lesions.
019d8bc3-60de-7405-a965-840491bd2778	MRI 2 region with no contrast	Radiology	Imaging	{D,SM}	MRI covering two adjacent regions without contrast for comprehensive evaluation.
019d8bc3-60de-7410-973a-55fcf2b868dc	MRI 2 region with contrast	Radiology	Imaging	{D,SM}	MRI of two regions with contrast for maximum diagnostic information.
019d8bc3-60de-741f-92fa-9341936b3589	Myelogram - 1 Region	Radiology	Imaging	{D,SM}	Contrast study of spinal canal for evaluation of spinal cord and nerve root compression.
019d8bc3-60de-742a-b752-f4f6d7620b20	Myocardial perfusion imaging	Nuclear Medicine	Imaging	{D,SM}	Nuclear stress test assessing blood flow to heart muscle for coronary artery disease diagnosis.
019d8bc3-60de-7434-9d57-fe47ad52e631	Percutaneous Biopsy - CT Scan Guide	Radiology	Procedure	{D,SM}	CT-guided needle biopsy for precise sampling of deep lesions, tumors, or masses.
019d8bc3-60de-7470-b23b-2d2929cef6af	Progesterone (Prog)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures progesterone levels for fertility assessment, ovulation confirmation, and pregnancy monitoring.
019d8bc3-60de-747c-8461-1ade7172cb6a	Prostate Specific Antigen (PSA)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Tumor marker for prostate cancer screening, diagnosis, and monitoring of treatment response.
019d8bc3-60de-748a-96f0-97ae19337c70	Serum Adrenocorticotropic Hormone (ACTH)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures ACTH levels for differential diagnosis of Cushing syndrome and adrenal insufficiency.
019d8bc3-60de-7495-9eee-5ea02e55cd8e	Serum Beta-Human Chorionic Gonadotropin (HCG)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Quantitative hCG for pregnancy confirmation, gestational age estimation, and trophoblastic tumor monitoring.
019d8bc3-60de-74a1-b045-a4134393cb64	Serum Ferritin	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures iron storage protein for diagnosis of iron deficiency anemia and hemochromatosis.
019d8bc3-60de-74b4-835d-c36561501889	Serum Iron (Fe)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures serum iron levels for iron deficiency, overload, and anemia evaluation.
019d8bc3-60de-74c3-85b0-a5b720402c08	Serum Lactate Dehydrogenase (LDH)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Non-specific marker for cell injury, elevated in hemolysis, malignancy, and tissue damage.
019d8bc3-60de-74cd-b4f0-0a0ec873c8ab	Serum Prolactin (PRL)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures prolactin levels for diagnosis of hyperprolactinemia, pituitary tumors, and infertility.
019d8bc3-60de-74d9-ab21-6b3d7dd9010e	Serum vitamin B12 and folate levels	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures B12 and folate for diagnosis of megaloblastic anemia and nutritional deficiencies.
019d8bc3-60de-74e7-8b0b-c0fb5e094db2	Testosterone	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Measures testosterone levels for hypogonadism, infertility, and endocrine disorder diagnosis.
019d8bc3-60de-74f1-828a-1d087c4d078e	Thyroid Function Test (TSH)	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Thyroid Stimulating Hormone - primary screening test for thyroid disorders.
019d8bc3-60de-74f8-a288-42b75ad853be	Thyroid Profile	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Comprehensive thyroid panel including TSH, FT3, FT4, and sometimes antibodies for full thyroid assessment.
019d8bc3-60de-7506-8212-768f1df3d2da	T3	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Total or free Triiodothyronine for thyroid function assessment, especially in T3 thyrotoxicosis.
019d8bc3-60de-7513-80a1-7d82cee7315b	T4	Biochemistry	Lab	{D,SM}	Total or free Thyroxine for thyroid function assessment in hypothyroidism and hyperthyroidism.
019d8bc3-60de-751f-9904-f9c24b81d4fe	Venogram - 1 Region	Radiology	Imaging	{D,SM}	Contrast study of veins in one region for diagnosis of deep vein thrombosis and venous insufficiency.
019d8bc3-60de-752a-8b55-ffadccc585b1	Viral serology	Microbiology	Lab	{D,SM}	Detection of antibodies against specific viruses (HIV, hepatitis, EBV, CMV) for diagnosis of viral infections.
